author: JohnFLob
title: Re: Obamacare signups are down? HuffPo’s Sam Stein says it’s ‘sabotage’!
text:
— Stephen Miller (@redsteeze) February 3, 2017 
Trouble in Obamacare paradise? The sabotage of Ocare appears to have worked. Sign ups went from nearly 790k in last week of 2016 to about 375k in last two weeks of 2017 
— Sam Stein (@samsteinhp) February 3, 2017 
Sabotage, Sam? Really? @samsteinhp The "sabotage"? You mean the one caused by the people who wrote such an awful, unsustainable law that was imploding from day 1?
